==Home media==
The first seven episodes were released on [[DVD]] on May 30, 2006 in [[DVD region code#1|Region 1]] from [[Lionsgate Home Entertainment]] in a single-disc release entitled ''ALF and The Beanstalk and Other Classic Fairy Tales''.

